(20, 1, 'Lemilice', 'Lemilica TMT-9000S', 0, 'Lemilica-TMT-9000S', 'Thermaltronics', 'tmt-9000s.jpg', 'Curie Heat Technologija koji radi na 13.56MHz, Visok termički oporavak i performanse, Dva izlaza za rad i LCD ekranom, Koristi T seriju vrhova, Nije potrebna kalibracija ili obuka operatera, Snaga: 40W', 'Lemilica TMT-9000S zasnovana je na tehnologiji Curie Heat koja reaguje na toplotne potrebe svakog lemnog spoja. Samopodešavanjem snage (toplote) ispunjava tačni zahtev komponente i materijala za lemljenje na PCB ploči. Brzina dostizanje snage (temperature) za rad je oko 4 sekunde. Na samoj stanici moguće je priključiti razlemljivač (pištolj) i termo pincetu. Postoji mogućnost naizmeničnog rada na stanici za dve različite aplikacije. Veoma pogodan za složene zahtevne samih aplikacija. - Opširnije informacije za razlemljivač (pištolj) i termo pincete možete videti u podkategoriji \"Propratna oprema i materijal\". - Izbor vrhova iz Serije M mozete videti na \"Detaljnije na sajtu proizvođača\"', 1, 'http://www.thermaltronics.com/tmt-9000s.php'),
(21, 1, 'Lemilice', 'Lemilica TMT-5000S', 1, 'Lemilica-TMT-5000S', 'Thermaltronics', 'tmt-5000s.jpg', 'Curie Heat Technologi koji radi na 13,56MHz, Jedan izlaz za rad, Koristi T seriju vrhova, Lagan i kompaktan, Nije potrebna kalibracija ili obuka operatera, Snaga: 30W', 'Lemilica TMT-5000S zasnovana je na tehnologiji Curie Heat koja reaguje na toplotne potrebe svakog lemnog spoja. Samopodešavanjem snage (toplote) ispunjava tačni zahtev komponente i materijala za lemljenje na PCB ploči. Brzina dostizanje snage (temperature) za rad je oko 5 sekundi. Na samoj stanici moguće je priključiti razlemljivač (pištolj) i termo pincetu. - Opširnije informacije za razlemljivač (pištolj) i termo pincete možete videti u podkategoriji \"Dodatna oprema i materijal\". - Izbor vrhova iz Serije T mozete videti na \"Detaljnije na sajtu proizvođača\"', 0, 'http://www.thermaltronics.com/tmt-5000s.php'),
(22, 1, 'Propratni-materijal', 'Automatski dodavač kalaja AF-KIT', 0, 'Automatski-dodavac-kalaja-AF-KIT', 'Thermaltronics', 'af-kit-1.jpg', 'Podesiva brzina i dužina dodavanja kalajne žice,  Podesivo uvlačenje kalajne žice, Uredjaj omogućava preciznu kontrolu, Povećava efikasnost', 'Automatski dodavač kalaja AF-KIT omogućava rad u jednoj ruci za vreme lemljenja. Komplet se isporučuje kao dodatak postojećim Thermaltronics sistemima za ručno lemljenje.', 0, 'http://www.thermaltronics.com/af-kit.php'),
(23, 6, 'Propratni-materijal', 'Automatski čistač vrha TMT-ASTC', 0, 'Automatski-cistac-vrha-TMT-ASTC', 'Thermaltronics', 'tmt-astc100.jpg', 'Uklanja sa vrha kalaj i oksidacije, Lagan i kompaktan, Lako se čisti i održava', 'Automatski čistač vrha TMT-ASTC ukljanja ostatke kalaja i oksidacije sa vrha. Sistem se sastoji iz dve visoko kvalitetne mesingane četke, koje se okreću u suprotnim smerovima.', 0, 'thermaltronics.com/tmt-astc100.php'),
(24, 1, 'Propratni-materijal', 'Dodavač kalajne žice TMT-SSH100', 0, 'Dodavac-kalajne-zice-TMT-SSH100', 'Thermaltronics', 'tmt-ssh100.jpg', 'Precizno dodavanje kalajne žice, Kontinuirano pušta žicu za lemljenje, Operater ne mora da ručno radi sa žicom, Precizno i udobno lemljenje', 'Držač kalajne žice TMT-SSH100 koristi visokokvalitetni sistem koji pomaže da se glatko i brzo doziraju žice za lemljenje.', 0, 'http://www.thermaltronics.com/tmt-ssh100.php'),
(25, 4, 'p-and-p', 'Desktop Pick&place KAYO-D2V-25S', 0, 'Desktop-Pickplace-KAYO-D2V-25S', 'KAYO', 'KAYO-D2V-25S.jpg', 'Drawer type computer and driver integrated, Disassembled chassis, easy to handling, HD industrial camera, precisely identify 0402, Intelligent remounting design, Component auxiliary box design, Software is easy to understand and use', 'KAYO-D2V-25S is the classic of desktop dual-head SMT pick and placement machine. High precision, more reasonable mechanical design, easy operation, stable running, adapting air-operated feeder, automatic vision system, automatic detection materials shortage. Suitable for mounting most of the SMD components, such as 0402 0603 0805 1206 1210 3528 5050 SOP QFN, etc.', 0, 'http://en.kayosmt.com/index.php/Show/index/cid/342/id/289.html'),
(26, 4, 'p-and-p', 'Pick&Place KAYO-A4', 0, 'PickPlace-KAYO-A4', 'KAYO', 'KAYO-A4.jpg', 'High Precision, The max. mounting speed: 7000CPH, Average mounting speed: 5000CPH,  Full Automation: With rail guide,  Strong Stability: Panasonic Servo Motor and Drive, Could effectively mount 0402-5050 components', 'High Precision: Equipped with 6pcs of cameras: 1pc of Mark recognition camera, 1pc of 500 million pixels high precision recognition camera, and 4pcs of synchronous high-speed recognition cameras, could effectively mount 0402-5050 components, LED beads, diodes, transistors, SOP, 40mm*40mm range pin pitch ≥0.3mm chip QFP, BGA etc.  Strong Stability: Panasonic Servo Motor and Drive, TBI high-precision grinding ball screw rod + heavy-duty linear guide, Japan Vacuum generator, JUKI high-precise nozzles, automatic feeding integrated system and high-configuration IPC - High precision, strong stability, promise 24-hour mounting stably.', 0, 'http://en.kayosmt.com/index.php/Show/index/cid/342/id/321.html'),
(27, 4, 'p-and-p', 'Pick&Place KAYO-A4L', 0, 'PickPlace-KAYO-A4L', 'KAYO', 'KAYOA4L.jpg', 'High Precision: Equipped with 6pcs of cameras, Fast Speed: the max. mounting speed: 8000CPH, average mounting speed: 6000CPH, Strong Stability: Panasonic Servo Motor and Drive', 'Optimized multi-functional conveyor (best positioning + no impact stopping), adopt a laser sensor rather than mechanical stopper to position. No rely on the PCB board size, shape, achieve the best positioning and no impact stop.\r\nHigh Precision: Equipped with 6pcs of cameras: 1pc of Mark, 1pc of high precision, and 4pcs of high-speed recognition cameras, could effectively mount 0402-5050 components, beads, diodes, transistors, SOP, 45mm*45mm range pin pitch ≥0.3mm chip QFP-256, BGA etc.\r\nTBI precise linear guide and ball screw, Japan Vacuum generator, JUKI high-precise nozzles, automatic feeding integrated system and high-configuration IPC - High precision, strong stability, promise 24-hour mounting stably.', 1, 'http://en.kayosmt.com/index.php/Show/index/cid/342/id/290.html'),
(28, 4, 'p-and-p', 'Pick&Place KAYO-1706-3DSG', 0, 'PickPlace-KAYO-1706-3DSG', 'KAYO', 'KAYO-1706-3DSG.jpg', '6 heads, 8pcs of cameras, Quick positioning, Low noise, High precision, Imported heavy-duty linear guide', 'Three-section transmitting boards-automatic connection from left to right (The first section is waiting for mounting, the second section is responsible for mounting (When the PCB board finishes mounting and transmits to the third section, the first section also receives the demand to prepare a new boards simultaneously.), the third section transmits the board from p&p machine to reflow oven. Effectively save time of transmitting boards and improve efficiency.\r\nPanasonic Servo Motor and Drive, TBI precise linear guide, Japan Vacuum generator, JUKI high-precise nozzles, automatic feeding integrated system and high-configuration IPC - High precision, strong stability, promise 24-hour mounting stably.', 0, 'http://en.kayosmt.com/index.php/Show/index/cid/342/id/291.html'),
(29, 4, 'p-and-p', 'Pick&Place KAYO-A8L', 0, 'PickPlace-KAYO-A8L', 'KAYO', 'KAYO-A8L.jpg', '8 heads, Total 10pcs of cameras, Adopt imported JUKI nozzle spring buffer, Precision control error can reach 0.018mm, Adopt Japan Panasonic A6 series AC servo motor, With two 17” displays', ' Change the traditional way of positive pressure turning into negative pressure to pick up components, built-in high-efficiency & energy-saving vacuum pump and vacuum tank, equipped with the latest r&d vacuum damage system. Greatly improve the efficiency of picking up the components, eliminate the noise caused by positive pressure turning into negative pressure, delay and reduce the frequency of air compressor start-up, effectively improve the life of air compressor. Can hold 70pcs of 8mm pneumatic feeders simultaneously, reserved 38 electric feeder interface, could switch feeder type at random, also could be electric, pneumatic feeder mixture. Accurately mount 0201-5050 resistance, LED lamp beads, diodes, transistor, SOP, chip QFP-256, 45mm*45mm range QFP, BGA etc.', 0, 'http://en.kayosmt.com/index.php/Show/index/cid/342/id/292.html'),
(30, 2, 'Manualni-printeri', 'Manualni štampač za SMD - KAYO-P1000', 0, 'Manualni-stampac-za-SMD-KAYO-P1000', 'KAYO', 'stampac3.jpg', 'Nanošenje paste za lemljenje na jednostranoj i dvostranoj PCB ploči, Max veličina PCB: 250 x 400mm, Max veličina šablona: 300 x 400mm, Max visina dvostrane ploče: 80 mm, Podešavanje šablona: vertikalno/horizontalno  +/-10mm, Visina platforme: 190mm', 'Manualni štampač za nanošenje paste za lemljenje na PCB ploče. Nanošenje paste ili lepka za lemljenje na jednostranoj i dvostranoj PCB ploči. Uredjaj je izrađen od nerđajućeg čelika. Pozicioniranje PCB ploča vrši se na pričvrsnim pinovima. Brzo podešavanje šablona po X,Y osi i visini pomoću prikladnih ručki. Pouzdano pričvršćivanje šablona sa 4 vijka. Poravnavanje PCB-a i šablona.', 0, 'http://en.kayosmt.com/index.php/Show/index/cid/345/id/283.html'),
(31, 4, 'Stencile-printeri', 'Polu-automatski štampač KAYO-5088', 0, 'Polu-automatski-stampac-KAYO-5088', 'KAYO', '1KAYO-5088.jpg', 'Microcomputer control, Touch screen display, Menu operating interface,  Using two-hand button switch operation, Safe and reliable, Scraper pressure adjustable', ' Touch screen menu can independently set the whole steel net pause time up and down PCB positioning methods include reference hole positioning, reference edge positioning, reference hole & edge positioning at the same time, template positioning, etc Touch screen with time display function, printing times count function automatically, screen protection function. With scraper speed adjusment function and emergency stop safety function Printing Mode: single, double, second start (menu settings optional). Printing working status: automatic / semi-automatic / jogging three printing status (menu settings optional). Cast iron table, work smoothly, no jitter phenomenon.', 0, 'http://en.kayosmt.com/index.php/Show/index/cid/345/id/280.html'),
(32, 4, 'Stencile-printeri', 'Polu-automatski štampač KAYO-5088C', 0, 'Polu-automatski-stampac-KAYO-5088C', 'KAYO', '1KAYO5088C.jpg', 'Microcomputer control, Touch screen display, Menu operating interface, Scraper speed adjustment function, Emergency stop safety function', 'Scraper pressure adjustable (according to the length of the different types of scraper blade, adjust the pressure to the steel). Equipped with the inverter speed control system, scraper running speed is steady. Using two-hand button switch operation, safe and reliable. Touch screen menu can independently set the whole steel net pause time up and down. PCB positioning methods include reference hole positioning, reference edge positioning, reference hole & edge positioning at the same time.Printing Mode: single, double, second start (menu settings optional)Printing working status: automatic / semi-automatic / jogging three printing status (menu settings optional). Cast iron table, work smoothly, no jitter phenomenon.', 0, 'http://en.kayosmt.com/index.php/Show/index/cid/345/id/320.html'),
(33, 4, 'Stencile-printeri', 'Polu-automatski štampač KAYO-5088L', 0, 'Polu-automatski-stampac-KAYO-5088L', 'KAYO', '5088L.jpg', 'Scraper pressure adjustable, Safe and reliable,  Microcomputer control, Touch screen display, Menu operating interface, Equipped with the inverter speed control system', 'Touch screen menu can independently set the whole steel net pause time up and down. PCB positioning methods include reference hole positioning, reference edge positioning, reference hole & edge positioning at the same time, template positioning, etc. Touch screen with time display function, printing times count function automatically, screen protection function. With scraper speed adjustment function and emergency stop safety function. Printing Mode: single, double, second start (menu settings optional). Printing working status: automatic / semi-automatic / jogging three printing status (menu settings optional). Cast iron table, work smoothly, no jitter phenomenon.', 0, 'http://en.kayosmt.com/index.php/Show/index/cid/345/id/284.html'),
(34, 4, 'Stencile-printeri', 'Automatski štampač KAYO-400', 0, 'Automatski-stampac-KAYO-400', 'KAYO', '1KAYO400.jpg', 'Compatible with a wide range of PCB, High precision printing resolution, Automatic stencil frame positioning, Automatic PCB correction, Automatic scraper pressure adjustment, Automatic stencil frame cleaning', 'Adopt independently developed floating printing head, the automatic adjustment system of the programmable scraper pressure, automatically balance the scraper pressure, with precise pressure control, can achieve the perfect solder paste forming effect. Programmable motor controls scraper and stencil frame separation speed and stroke, can flexibly achieve a variety of demoulding methods. Multi-functional PCB fixed positioning system, PCB positioning convenient, fast and accurate. Up and down visual positioning system. Built-in image processing system. Support 2D, SPC function. The printing translation is driven by the motor directly connected to the timing belt.', 0, 'http://en.kayosmt.com/index.php/Show/index/cid/345/id/285.html'),
(35, 4, 'Stencile-printeri', 'Automatski štampač KAYO-450', 0, 'Automatski-stampac-KAYO-450', 'KAYO', '1KAYO450.jpg', 'Precision, Special adjustment platform, Using windows XP operating system, Programmable suspension self-adjusting stepper motor, PCB positioning system, Automatic cleaning structure, High adaptability steel mesh frame clamping system, Electronic control s', 'Independent direct-connected stepper motor control, built-in precision pressure control system, can accurately measure the blade original pressure value, without consider blade type, length, weight or thickness changes. Programmable realizes printing process flexible; Designed according to front and rear blade required different pressure & the stability of the lift to prevent solder paste leakage and the blade with a certain flexibility of the clamping design, blade pressure, lifting speed, printing speed, printing range are adjusted through software, and provide customers a variety of stripping module ways to adapt PCB with different tin requirements, providing a good printing control platform for customers. Realize the printing of various meshes’ sizes (370mm x 470mm ~ 737mm x 737mm), and can realize the rapid replacement model in the production process; Y direction automatic positioning. Adopt self-developed modular integrated circuits, safe, easy maintenance; use the most advanced industrial control system, achieve to modify the parameters during operation.', 0, 'http://en.kayosmt.com/index.php/Show/index/cid/345/id/282.html'),
(36, 4, 'Stencile-printeri', 'Automatski štampač KAYO-600', 0, 'Automatski-stampac-KAYO-600', 'KAYO', '1KAYO600.jpg', 'Simple and reliable structure, Adaptive PCB thickness, PCB positioning system, New light path system, Dry cleaning, Wet washing, Vacuum three cleaning methods, High adaptability steel mesh frame clamping system,  English user interface', 'Dedicated math model with Repeatability±15μm (± 0.0005 \") @ 6 σ, Cp≥2.0. Ensure the machine to achieve high precision alignment.  Intelligent and fast matching of different thickness PCB boards with their transmission and clamping mechanisms. Designed for the different front and rear blade pressure requirements and the stability of the lift, to prevent the solder paste from leaking and the blade has a certain elastic clamping design, the blade pressure, lifting speed, printing speed, printing range are all adjusted by software, provide customers with a variety of demoulding methods to adapt to different tin-plated PCB boards. Rail-type intelligent scraper system for improving operational stability and extending service life.', 1, 'http://en.kayosmt.com/index.php/Show/index/cid/345/id/281.html'),
(37, 4, 'Peći-lemljenje', 'Reflow peć KAYO-RF330', 0, 'Reflow-pec-KAYO-RF330', 'KAYO', 'KAYO-RF330.jpg', '3 Heating Zones, Stainless steel conveyor belt, Power saving, Exhaust port, Alarm protection function, ', 'Adopt the latest streamlined design, the appearance of the whole machine is integration, the upper, middle and lower can be arbitrarily disassembled and assembled to facilitate customers upstairs and downstairs, all configuration interface using plug-in type, to facilitate future maintenance. Built-in rotating flywheel, free to transfer. Without trouble by power outages, making the temperature of the heating zone fully radiating, the thermal expansion coefficient of the stainless steel mesh belt are same, effectively extend the service life of the equipment.', 0, 'http://en.kayosmt.com/index.php/Show/index/cid/336/id/317.html'),
(38, 4, 'Peći-lemljenje', 'Reflow peć KAYO-RF430', 0, 'Reflow-pec-KAYO-RF430', 'KAYO', 'KAYO-RF430.jpg', '4 Heating Zones, 8pcs of controlling meters, Italian high-temperature high-speed motor, The intelligent micro-computer precision controller, Reliable and smooth transmission system, Stable and reliable electrical control system', 'High efficiency and energy-save Swedish 110V nickel chromium heating pipe is used in heating system (replacement within three year), radiation power peak wavelength 4UM, equipped with surface reflector, high thermal efficiency, rapid heating speed, specially-made strong hot air cycle structure system, making PCB and components heating equally, completely eliminate the shadow effect. Adopt imported high-current solid-state relay non-contact output, safe and reliable, combined with the temperature controller which has unique fuzzy control function, always monitoring the outside temperature and heat value changes, control heating components with minimize pulse , fast response to ensure temperature control accuracy ±1℃, the error of inside temperature distribution ±2℃. Temperature distribution in the length direction conform to IPC standards.', 0, 'http://en.kayosmt.com/index.php/Show/index/cid/336/id/316.html'),
(39, 4, 'Peći-lemljenje', 'Reflow peć KAYO-RF530', 0, 'Reflow-pec-KAYO-RF530', 'KAYO', 'KAYO-RF530.jpg', '5 Heating Zones, PID overall temperature control, Easy to operate, Ultra high temperature resistant motor, Precisely layout distribution box, High quality fan', 'Thickening aluminum plate could be more evenly distributed heat, better heat dissipation, more durable. The distribution box is precisely layout in the rear side of the machine for easy maintenance. It is extremely safe in both materials and design. Equipped with air switch, fuse, over temperature protection. Oven adopt 800 degree High temperature resistant & corrosion resistant finish. Adopt ultra high temperature resistant motor, fast heat dissipation, high safety, greatly reducing the failure caused by excessive temperature. External heating zones instrument and transport adjustment, which is more convenient for the customers to detect the temperature change and speed adjusting status, make sure the quality of the soldering. Newest PID micro-computer overall temperature control system, which provides precise temperature control, quick heating-up, low energy consumption and high efficiency.', 0, 'http://en.kayosmt.com/index.php/Show/index/cid/336/id/318.html'),
(40, 4, 'Peći-lemljenje', 'Reflow peć KAYO-RF630', 0, 'Reflow-pec-KAYO-RF630', 'KAYO', 'KAYO-RF630.jpg', '6 Heating Zones, Reliable and smooth transmission system, Advanced and long-life heating system, 12pcs of controlling meters,  Special stainless steel type mesh belt', 'High efficiency and energy-save Swedish nickel chromium heating pipe is used in heating system, radiation power peak wavelength 4UM, equipped with surface reflector, high thermal efficiency, rapid heating speed, specially-made strong hot air cycle structure system, making PCB and components heating equally, completely eliminate the shadow effect. Transmission system adopts Japan Matsushita stepless speed motor, adjustable belt speed stepless speed governor, smoothly operating matched up with 1:150 turbine reducer, speed 0-2000mm /min stepless adjustable, and also accurate digital Line speed indication.  Adopt independent roller structure and support, combined with supporting stainless steel mesh belt, running smoothly, precise speed up to ±20mm/min', 0, 'http://en.kayosmt.com/index.php/Show/index/cid/336/id/315.html'),
(41, 4, 'Peći-lemljenje', 'Reflow peć KAYO-610L', 0, 'Reflow-pec-KAYO-610L', 'KAYO', 'KAYO-610L.jpg', '6 Heating Zones, Forced impact convection, Completely meet the lead-free process, High temperature control accuracy and low power consumption, Suitable for CSB and BGA component welding', '6 Heating Zones, Forced impact convection, Completely meet the lead-free process, High temperature control accuracy and low power consumption, Suitable for CSB and BGA component welding. 6 Heating Zones, Forced impact convection, Completely meet the lead-free process, High temperature control accuracy and low power consumption, Suitable for CSB and BGA component welding.', 0, 'http://en.kayosmt.com/index.php/Show/index/cid/336/id/263.html'),
(42, 4, 'Peći-lemljenje', 'Reflow peć KAYO-RF835', 0, 'Reflow-pec-KAYO-RF835', 'KAYO', 'KAYO-RF835.jpg', '8 Heating Zones, Patented Innovative Insulation System, Adopt precise industrial meter control,  Multi-point air injection principle, Strong forced cooling system, Multi-point air injection principle', 'Heating adopts imported special long-life wound-rotor nickel chromium heating wire, high thermal efficiency and sensitivity, small thermal inertia, the temperature controlling accuracy in each temperature zone is ±1℃; directly heating cycle air, heating up quickly, from room temperature to setting temperature about 15 minutes. Imported Taiwan Sanyue radiating type high temperature motor, directly driving hot air heating, hot air balanced, small vibration, small noise. Special transmission rail guide, made of high temperature and wear resistance stainless steel, high rigidity, lasting non-deformation. All the electrical components are imported, all the signal lines are shielded, to make the entire controlling system more stable and reliable.', 0, 'http://en.kayosmt.com/index.php/Show/index/cid/336/id/314.html'),
