(73, 5, 'Mikroskopi', 'Video Mikroskop SANXO-scope HD U4 Express', 0, 'Video-Mikroskop-SANXO-scope-HD-U4-Express', 'C.I.F', 'digital-microscopes-hd-sanxo.jpg', 'Build with  an IDS Imaging 18MPixel camera, The tunable lens adds features for the user, New much faster focus approach by applying the focusing method on the map, The focus is done in a couple of milliseconds', 'Range of digital video-microscopes conceived by Sanxo that offers a complete configuration with a close-up high quality image in direct inspection. They produce a frame rate from 35 to 62 FPS for the Sanxo-scope HD U4 and from 45 to 70 FPS for the Sanxo-scope HD U4 Express.', 0, 'https://cif.fr/en/digital-microscopes-hd-sanxo/412-digital-microscopes-hd-sanxo.html'),
(74, 5, 'Mikroskopi', 'Video Mikroskop SANXO-SCOPE HD U5 HYPER', 0, 'Video-Mikroskop-SANXO-SCOPE-HD-U5-HYPER', 'C.I.F', 'digital-microscopes-hd-sanxo.jpg', 'DIGITAL MICROSCOPE HD, Built with an IDS Imaging 2.3MPixel camera, The tunable lens adds features for the use, 100-150 FPS, ', 'The digital video-microscopes conceived by Sanxo offers a complete configuration with a close-up high quality image in direct inspection. The Sanxo-scope U5 hyper produces a frame rate from 100 to 150 fps. It was initially conceived as a manual inspection workshop for electronic cards. It is robust, accessible and can be used for any other object.', 0, 'https://cif.fr/en/digital-microscopes-hd-sanxo/414-digital-microscopes-hd-sanxo.html'),
(75, 5, 'Mikroskopi', 'Video Mikroskop SANXO-SCOPE HD U6', 0, 'Video-Mikroskop-SANXO-SCOPE-HD-U6', 'C.I.F', 'digital-microscopes-hd-sanxo.jpg', 'It is built with an IDS Imaging 3.1MPixel camera, The tunable lens adds features for the user, The focus is done in a couple of milliseconds', 'Therefor a 3D imaging of the surface is generated to give a better understanding and a clear visualization of the object. The digital video-microscopes conceived by Sanxo offers a complete configuration with a close-up high quality image in direct inspection. The Sanxo-scope U6 produces a frame rate from 57 to 80 FPS.', 0, 'https://cif.fr/en/digital-microscopes-hd-sanxo/415-digital-microscopes-hd-sanxo.html');
